Class Bicycle

java.lang.Object
net.etf.project.model.vehicles.Vehicle
net.etf.project.model.vehicles.Bicycle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ICharging
public class Bicycle extends Vehicle
Represents a bicycle in the vehicle rental system. A bicycle has a specific range and is a subclass of Vehicle.

      public double calculateRepairCost()
      Calculates the repair cost for the bicycle based on the number of malfunctions and a specific coefficient. The repair cost is calculated using the purchase price of the bicycle, the number of malfunctions, and the coefficient defined for bicycles.
